<p>This atom package installs the KartaVR 3rd party supporting libraries that are used to power the "Script > KartaVR > " menu item based tools.</p>

<p>The Reactor "Bin" Cateogry packages are installed on your system in the Reactor managed folder of:<br>
<a href="file://Reactor:/Deploy/Bin/">Reactor:/Deploy/Bin/</a></p>

